Feedback: pls check if you can make the withdrawal process any smoother in the app.
To withdraw, one has to exit the app to obtain the authenticator code (usually on the same mobile device). When re-opening, we are required to log in again (in my case biometrics). Often, we are also pushed back to the main menu and have to re-navigate. That process, including loading times, often takes too long and by the time we are at the point to enter the biometrics code, it has already expired. 
Last time it took me 5 attempts until i was quick enough. 
Samsung Galaxy S21
